column2: SELECT top #    o.objid,m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,     o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2,    m.apstar_id, m.apogee_id,params.*, paramerrs.*, elemsALL.*  into mydb.MyTable_# from apogeeStar AS m  OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n      JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid   JOIN aspcapStar a on a.apstar_id = m.apstar_id   CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParams(a.aspcap_id) params CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParamErrs(a.aspcap_id) paramerrs   CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapElemsAll( a.aspcap_id ) elemsALL
